description:
Following on from the last episode, we learn about Ellen White's vision. Soon after the Great Disappointment, Ellen prayed and received a vision from God. How do you respond when you are called by God? This simple but huge question was something that Ellen White had to grapple with that had huge consequences for the future of the Advent believers. The gift of prophecy would be one of the means that God used to guide His people through some turbulent and crucial years.

To find out more information about Ellen White read our extended article on our website.
